name: Basic Cost of Living
description:
The basic monthly cost of living for the artist, based on his current situation: renting a 412 sqft 1br apartment in downtown Denver, storage for art studio, food, insurance, clothing. Does not reflect unforeseen medical expenses, cost of maintaining a creative practice, or other factors yet to be actualized.

Edition size calculated based on the number of months remaining in the artist's life assuming the average life expectancy of a male US citizen (80).
